## Route Groups (middleware)

```
auth only:
  /calls, /placements (scoped by role within controllers)

auth + role:admin,account_manager:
  /dashboard, /clients, /consultants, /timesheets, /invoices,
  /ledger, /reports, /budget, /payroll (index + api/dashboard + api/consultants)

auth + role:admin:
  /admin/users, /settings, /audit-log, /backups,
  /payroll/upload, /payroll/recompute-margins,
  /payroll/api/aggregate, /payroll/api/goal, /payroll/api/mappings
```

When adding new routes, match the correct middleware group тАФ do not invent a new one.

